{"tid":326174,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[日文歌]點解無乜人提起GARNiDELiA？","createTime":"2017-07-17T18:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T02:53:57.000Z","uid":1863,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b9274e513100344fe7308393ba349519c79103b5","tid":326174,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/025353_a41da96a938ccf9a7d7cceef7b24283a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F025353_a41da96a938ccf9a7d7cceef7b24283a.jpg&h=d551d103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGARNiDELiA（ガルニデリア）為日本索尼音樂娛樂旗下SACRA MUSIC所屬的音樂團體。簡稱為「ガルニデ」，由歌手MARiA（水橋舞）和作曲家toku（阿部尚徳）組成。 團體名稱的由來為「Le Palais Garnier de Maria（法語為MARiA的歌劇場之意）」，與toku的出生年份同時發現的小行星小惑星（Cordelia）」中的文字所組合而成。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲分享 : <br />\nGARNiDELiA - Speed Star <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GQlky845kk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGQlky845kk8&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJigHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5064daae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GQlky845kk8</a><br />\nGARNiDELiA - 桃園戀曲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QtuWTHHzfXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQtuWTHHzfXE&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJigHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=72261610\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QtuWTHHzfXE</a><br />\nGARNiDELiA - 極樂淨土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BEULybZnLO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBEULybZnLO8&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJigHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3c7e26a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BEULybZnLO8</a><br />\nGARNiDELiA - LAMB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Oc6EW6gGJC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOc6EW6gGJC8&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJigHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=844b229b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Oc6EW6gGJC8</a><br />\n<br />\n這裏有水橋舞，這裏就是極樂淨土！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/025708_929594a7e1a714bdf10c79a7b027a161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F025708_929594a7e1a714bdf10c79a7b027a161.jpg&h=db0c7cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">GARNiDELiA！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"d6df673d5056e0eed43884cbd197213d7c8cc4fe","tid":326174,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:12:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">GARNiDELiA！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"e403945ea9ad9c75582428b7b9ee0fea1fac7fb6","tid":326174,"uid":128921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T20:13:17.000Z","msg":"Jw做咩走咗去日本"},{"pid":"80061f949ece5ebf929818243416352a8a3cd754","tid":326174,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T23:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">GARNiDELiA！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c645f4cc2a410ee4164c1725c56267e7ff15cc93","tid":326174,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T23:17:00.000Z","msg":"極樂淨土loop極都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79c03f209a7873d3bbf1f47203334982a4634be","tid":326174,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep